Package: loan
Type: Package
Title: Comprehensive Loan Portfolio Analysis and Credit Risk Management
Version: 0.1.0 
Authors@R: c(
    person("Rudolfs", "Kregers", email = "lordrudolf@inbox.lv", role = c("aut", "cre")))
Maintainer: Rudolfs Kregers <lordrudolf@inbox.lv>
Description: This package offers a comprehensive set of tools for loan portfolio analysis 
    and credit risk management. It features highly automated functions for streamlined 
    dataset handling, advanced analytics for assessing the value of client features, and 
    robust methods for underwriting workflow analysis. The package facilitates the 
    development of scorecards through integration with R base, caret, and tidymodels 
    frameworks, catering to a wide range of use cases in credit risk assessment.
